data.description: Welcome home! This energy-efficient 3-bed, 2-bath home on a desirable corner lot is now on the market! Enter to see a charming living room, vaulted ceilings, a custom palette, and practical tile flooring in the main areas. The kitchen has paneled cabinets, matching appliances, a convenient pantry, and a handy serving window. The main bedroom is a split, peaceful sanctuary offering direct backyard access, a walk-in closet, and a private bathroom with dual sinks. One of the secondary bedrooms also includes another walk-in closet! Serene backyard features a covered patio with extended pavers, a citrus tree, and ample space for gatherings. The solar panels save you money every month! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
